<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Nexus Systems — Community Security & Moderation' }) %></head>
<body>
  <div class="topnav">
    <div class="brand"><span class="dot"></span> Nexus Systems</div>
    <nav>
      <button class="icon-btn" id="theme-toggle-btn" title="Toggle theme">🌙</button>
      <a class="btn" href="<%= config.discordSupportUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">💬 Discord</a>
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a class="btn" href="/servers">My Servers</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/login">Login</a>
      <% } %>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <% if (maintenanceEnabled) { %>
    <div style="background:rgba(237,66,69,0.15);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(237,66,69,0.4);color:var(--red);text-align:center;padding:10px 20px;font-size:14px;">
      🔧 <strong>Maintenance:</strong> <%= maintenanceMessage || 'Some features may be temporarily unavailable.' %>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">✨ Free tier available &mdash; upgrade to VIP any time</div>
    <h1>Community security &amp; moderation,<br />built to run at scale.</h1>
    <p>AutoMod, anti-raid, anti-nuke, tickets, leveling, giveaways, starboard, and a full moderation suite — every setting configurable from a real web dashboard, not just slash commands.</p>
    <div class="cta">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="<%= inviteUrl %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener">➕ Add to your server</a>
      <a class="btn" href="<%= user ? '/servers' : '/login' %>">🖥️ Open Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-strip">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="num"><span class="status-pill" style="padding:2px 8px;"><span class="dot live"></span></span> Live</div>
      <div class="label">Bot Status</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="num"><%= guildCount %></div>
      <div class="label">Server<%= guildCount === 1 ? '' : 's' %> Protected</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="num">12+</div>
      <div class="label">Core Systems</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="num">24/7</div>
      <div class="label">Uptime Monitoring</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-heading" style="margin-top:70px;">
    <h2>Everything a growing community needs</h2>
    <p>One bot, one dashboard, zero guesswork — configure security, engagement, and support without memorizing a single slash command.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-grid">
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🛡️</div><h3>AutoMod</h3><p>Anti-spam, anti-link, anti-invite, regex banned words, caps &amp; emoji spam filters.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🚨</div><h3>Anti-Raid</h3><p>Join-burst detection, minimum account age gating, and one-click emergency lockdown.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🧨</div><h3>Anti-Nuke</h3><p>Catches mass channel/role deletion, mass kicks, and webhook abuse before real damage is done.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🔨</div><h3>Moderation</h3><p>Ban, kick, timeout, temp-ban, softban, mass-ban, warn, notes, purge — Discord or dashboard.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🎫</div><h3>Ticket Panels</h3><p>Unlimited custom ticket panels with categories, transcripts, and priority tagging.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">⭐</div><h3>Leveling</h3><p>XP, levels, role rewards, no-XP channels, and a full leaderboard.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🌟</div><h3>Starboard</h3><p>Highlight the best messages automatically.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🎉</div><h3>Giveaways &amp; Polls</h3><p>Role/level-gated giveaways with reroll support, plus quick polls.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">💬</div><h3>Custom Embeds</h3><p>Visual embed builder with a live Discord-style preview.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🎭</div><h3>Reaction Roles</h3><p>Self-assignable roles, including exclusive pick-one groups.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">📜</div><h3>Full Audit Trail</h3><p>Mod actions, message edits/deletes, joins/leaves, and the real Discord audit log.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">📈</div><h3>Analytics</h3><p>Moderation trends, top moderators, and activity charts per server.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">🖥️</div><h3>Live Console</h3><p>Real-time event stream straight from the bot process.</p></div>
    <div class="feature-card"><div class="icon">💎</div><h3>VIP Perks</h3><p>Unlimited limits, priority tickets, custom nickname &amp; theme color, 2x XP.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="home-footer">
    Nexus Systems — every server gets its own independent configuration. Running as <strong><%= botTag %></strong>.
  </div>

  <div id="toast-root"></div>
  <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
